rules_text: Whenever Caljak, Shadow of the End attacks, put a face-up exiled card into its owner’s graveyard. If that card is an artifact card, Caljak gains indestructible until end of turn. If that card is a creature card, put a +1/+1 counter on Caljak. If that card is an enchantment card, Caljak gains deathtouch until end of turn. If that card is a land card, you gain 3 life. If that card is none of those types, draw a card.
